</p><p class="- topic/p ">Put the joins in place and insert the 2x 4 screw
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-31A92965-8A0C-4E3F-A44C-AC4268704B21" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-F09E298A-21CE-4F0F-8BA4-A2D4992130E4-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F09E298A-21CE-4F0F-8BA4-A2D4992130E4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
